cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) to solve a navigation and spatial reasoning task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP. The second likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision) which deals with image analysis. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) which deals with intelligent agents and reasoning. The fourth likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) which deals with learning algorithms. The fifth likely category is cs.RO (Robotics) which deals with robot navigation and control.
